FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778105470
OL,3,CAlaska mega-tsunami was second largest
OL,4,Cever recorded
OL,6,FAlaska-based researcher Bretwood
OL,7,FHigman says the trend is concerning.
OL,9,F"When we look back over the last
OL,10,Fcouple 100 years, we see one of these
OL,11,Fhappening about every 20 years," said
OL,12,FHigman, co-founder and executive
OL,13,Fdirector of nonprofit Ground Truth
OL,14,FAlaska. But in the second-to-last
OL,15,Fdecade, that number had increased to
OL,16,Ftwo, and in the last decade it was six
OL,17,Fsuch events.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
