PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778105470
OL,3,CAlaska mega-tsunami was second largest
OL,4,Cever recorded
OL,6,F"We have what seems to be a tenfold
OL,7,Fincrease," Higman said. Despite the
OL,8,Fresults being based on limited data,
OL,9,Fhe said, "I think that pattern is
OL,10,Freal."
