PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778105470
OL,3,CAlaska mega-tsunami was second largest
OL,4,Cever recorded
OL,6,FIn addition to informing the cruise
OL,7,Findustry, other marine vessels, and
OL,8,Fpolicymakers, scientists say they hope
OL,9,Fa virtual jet ski will improve public
OL,10,Fawareness that these events are even
OL,11,Fhappening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
