PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778105470
OL,3,CAlaska mega-tsunami was second largest
OL,4,Cever recorded
OL,6,F"We can never remove the risk of
OL,7,Fsomething calamitous happening,"
OL,8,FShugar said. "I think that the onus is
OL,9,Fnot just on the cruise ship industries
OL,10,For the policymakers, but also on the
OL,11,Findividual citizens" to understand the
OL,12,Fpotential dangers involved with a
OL,13,Fcruise ship trip or a backpacking
OL,14,Fexpedition in the rugged wilderness
OL,15,Fnear receding glaciers and sloping
OL,16,Fmountains.
OL,18,FThese areas, he said, are "never going
OL,19,Fto be risk-free."
